The paper discusses the generalization of neural networks, which is a core topic in machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses visualization methods to explain the geometry of loss landscapes, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the curse of dimensionality, which is a common problem in optimization (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
